Job Description
Springfield Public Schools seeks outstanding candidates for assistant coaches for the following Spring sports at Thurston High School:
Baseball
Softball
Track & Field
Golf
Tennis
LaCrosse
Successful candidates will possess the following qualifications:
Coaching experience at the high school level in the sport/activity for which your are applying;
Knowledge of and experience in the sport/activity for which you are applying;
Ability and experience working with high school students;
Ability and experience working with parents, fellow coaches and school district staff;
Effective and positive communication skills;
Ability to work within school district guidelines and budget;
